1.0.name: wordpress/airplane
1.0.description: This plugin displays quotes from the classic movie "Airplane!" When activated you will randomly see a quote from "Airplane!" in the upper right of your admin screen on every page. It is based on the plugin "Hello, Dolly!", by Matt Mullenweg.
